        "content": "## CONFIG\nThe **only node you ever need to edit.**\n\n**Add a site:** Add a new field → Website4, Website5...\n**Remove a site:** Delete that field\n**Change email:** Edit alert_email\n**Change wait time:** Edit wait_secs (seconds)\n**Slow warning threshold:** Edit slow_threshold_ms (ms)\n**Max redirects:** Edit max_redirects\n\nField rules:\n- Must start with 'Website' (any case)\n- Duplicates auto-removed\n- Invalid URLs auto-skipped",
        "height": 536,
